        public static void saveDelimited(Dataset Data,
                 java.lang.String Filename,
                 java.lang.String Delimiter)
        Saves a Dataset as a string-delimited file. First row of file is the name of each attribute, subsequent lines are each attribute for each entry. Measured class is printed, if available.
        Parameters:
        Data - Dataset to be printed
        Filename - Desired filename
        Delimiter - Delimiter between words
